    <item>
      <title>FlappyBird之项目初始框架搭建</title>
      <link>https://game.longshilin.com/Entitas-FlappyBird-2020-10-12-FlappyBird-%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</link>
      <guid>https://game.longshilin.com/Entitas-FlappyBird-2020-10-12-FlappyBird-%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Oct 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;导入Entitas插件&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#导入Entitas插件&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;导入Entitas插件&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;导入Entitas插件&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;创建一个Unity空项目，然后导入Entitas-1.13.0.unitypackage资源文件 &lt;a href=&quot;https://longshilin.com/files/Entitas-1.13.0.unitypackage&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;附包下载地址&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Entitas插件导入之后，按快捷键 &lt;code&gt;Ctrl + Shift + G&lt;/code&gt; 生成Generated文件目录，再创建一个Features目录存放游戏逻辑代码，Scenes存放场景资源文件。&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <comments>https://game.longshilin.com/Entitas-FlappyBird-2020-10-12-FlappyBird-%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
